item.comments: Hello, I'm definitely looking forward to meeting some new friends in the area! If there is anyone driving to the picnic from downtown Boston or passing a T station, can you let me know? I'd like to catch a ride. Thanks! =)
Looking to catch a ride from anyone in the Fenway area or a nearby T station. Please let me know. Thanks!
I will be out of town !!! Have fun. Save me some winngs!!
When it comes to food, sure, why not! This will be my first time meeting the group.
Driving from Rhode Island so can pick some people up on the way.
Sorry, will have a college reunion in NYC that day. Have fun!
Anybody driving from Quincy that has room for 1? Please let me know, thx! :)
I'm new here, so bit nervous..
Just got to Boston last week and would love to make new friends. My friend and I (two girls) would like to catch a ride from back bay area or near a T station :)
